    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="什麼是Docker-Machine"><a href="#什麼是Docker-Machine" class="headerlink" title="什麼是Docker Machine"></a>什麼是Docker Machine</h1><p>能夠安裝Docker Engine 在 virtual hosts,並且能夠透過docker-machine管理它</p><p>支援: Mac or Windows box, on your company network, in your data center, or on cloud providers like Azure, AWS, or Digital Ocean.</p><hr><h3 id="Create-a-machine"><a href="#Create-a-machine" class="headerlink" title="Create a machine"></a>Create a machine</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">docker-machine create --driver virtualbox default</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="List-available-machines"><a href="#List-available-machines" class="headerlink" title="List available machines"></a>List available machines</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">docker-machine ls</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Get-the-environment-commands-for-your-new-VM"><a href="#Get-the-environment-commands-for-your-new-VM" class="headerlink" title="Get the environment commands for your new VM."></a>Get the environment commands for your new VM.</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">docker-machine env default</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
